Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.57,0:02:24.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优米尔大人 这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.82,0:02:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你即将穿在身上的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超振动装备
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:31.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问 超振动装备是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.02,0:02:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依靠超振动水晶的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.26,0:02:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展开特殊的力场
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.26,0:02:38.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将敌人的攻击全部弹开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.81,0:02:40.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究极的铠甲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.00,0:02:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要 要 要我当斗士什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.70,0:02:44.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.48,0:02:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可是为了你家人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.09,0:02:53.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.09,0:02:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这身铠甲的特点是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:12.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手的攻击越强 水晶的振动也会越强
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:14.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从而产生强大的力场
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我该做什么好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.03,0:03:20.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那老实站着就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.76,0:03:33.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:53.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是伟大的炼金术师·希昂的魔导石
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而能承受住这份力量的这副身体也真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:01.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是有点太敏感了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.10,0:04:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集钢铁山所有的知识和技术于一身
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.72,0:04:12.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大陆最强斗士计划
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.41,0:04:17.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于 其第一号实验体完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超振动战乙女·美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,号外 号外
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满版都是大事件的报道哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在各地被目击到的谜之光的真相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是否从月亮降临的最强斗士呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:41.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡里巴拉的深处 浓雾的密林中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.60,0:04:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探险队捕获了传说中的珍兽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.23,0:04:48.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 竟竟竟竟竟然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.61,0:04:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王大人的私生子疑云
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷鸣之夜出生的三胞胎姐妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:56.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欲知详情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请君解囊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.44,0:05:07.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老百姓就是喜欢看那种大事件 温迪
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.71,0:05:11.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以把这些提供给他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是我的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.07,0:05:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然也说不上是真实的报道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:21.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要早点到盖纳斯去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到美莉姆才行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.37,0:05:28.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.90,0:05:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总算追上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预言中出现的「命运之人」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.75,0:05:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该死的通缉犯 乖乖就范吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:47.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后就差「偶然」发生的「命运的再会」了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.05,0:05:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体里长出了奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.53,0:05:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让我采访下么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.76,0:05:59.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.61,0:06:06.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.50,0:06:09.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.01,0:06:12.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:14.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.09,0:06:15.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.73,0:06:18.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是通缉犯的同伙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.20,0:06:22.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为为为什么会变成这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究极的铠甲？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.55,0:06:31.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有配套的武器哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:34.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,预测敌人的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:36.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自动攻击敌人的究极武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超振动剑·无限利刃以及
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.19,0:06:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（Infinite Slasher）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.16,0:06:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超振动盾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.99,0:06:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 请鉴赏我之计划的成果吧 女王陛下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.07,0:06:54.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女王陛下？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.81,0:06:58.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得这玩意在实战中可没什么用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾丽娜 你要来试试吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.47,0:07:07.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.50,0:07:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平身
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.40,0:07:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.89,0:07:50.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃了姐姐大人一剑还能毫发无伤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.82,0:07:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我已经站不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.62,0:08:07.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.80,0:08:15.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤依特 已经安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.68,0:08:19.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥竟然是女人 真让我吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.36,0:08:22.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要再叫我哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.71,0:08:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会改的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为事到如今再改称呼又不合理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.54,0:08:31.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.64,0:08:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想死你了 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.86,0:08:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我啊 还以为再也见不到哥哥了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.22,0:08:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:58.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我离开克莱因城堡的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.73,0:09:07.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明想向你好好道别的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.14,0:09:09.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没能见到哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.37,0:09:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:21.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为现在和你重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.23,0:09:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤依特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.33,0:09:35.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要去找姐姐大人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.92,0:09:45.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我当斗士什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:47.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那身铠甲只有我才能脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.28,0:09:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优米尔大人 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:10:00.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不干的话 钱就泡汤了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.82,0:10:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,优米尔大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.20,0:10:15.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事 慌慌张张的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.79,0:10:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.99,0:10:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从返回的侦察队中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到了在索罗尔附近 目击到安妮洛特的报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.87,0:10:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到这么快就有实战测试的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.55,0:10:30.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前那个机器人及其主人也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.02,0:10:34.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤依特？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:40.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要赶快做好出击的准备了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.20,0:11:07.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你逃不出我的五指山
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:25.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我的确需要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:29.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为此要跟尤依特战斗的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:30.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.03,0:11:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快让路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.65,0:11:33.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真美丽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:39.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.65,0:11:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿着这铠甲 身体不能随心所欲地活动
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:01.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:22.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道到底该怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:26.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝将拯救所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请说出你的烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.58,0:12:41.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论你逃到哪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.71,0:12:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都可以根据铠甲上水晶发出的波动追踪到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.66,0:12:53.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 其实我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.11,0:12:57.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么声音
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:12:59.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这难道是 恶魔附体？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.27,0:13:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是因此而祈求上帝的庇护吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.31,0:13:29.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.51,0:13:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,违抗上帝的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.99,0:13:36.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上帝啊 请用您的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:38.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用神之光照耀她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.66,0:13:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救赎她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:45.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样做的话 会变得更激烈的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶魔在抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的恶魔 从她身上滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:02.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再打了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何都无法驱逐的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.17,0:14:10.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就将你视为异端 施以火刑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:21.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来在这
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.27,0:14:25.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:36.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.80,0:14:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是神圣的教会
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.08,0:14:43.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有中央教王厅的许可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为所欲为的话我会很困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.70,0:14:48.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是异端审问官·斯琪大人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:50.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那能请你高抬贵手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她还给我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.07,0:15:02.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美莉姆 给我过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要出击了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.38,0:15:18.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去击败反抗女王的安妮洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:20.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.27,0:15:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:27.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此分别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:30.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥又要去别的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.70,0:15:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.59,0:15:33.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:37.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去女王的首都·盖纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.94,0:15:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去盖纳斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.27,0:15:44.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去找被钢铁参谋·优米尔带走的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.32,0:15:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还必须夺回被偷走的妈妈的魔导石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:53.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.80,0:15:54.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.88,0:15:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.12,0:16:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再见吧 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:18.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事的家伙走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:22.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回终于可以跟姐姐来个「命运的再会」了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:58.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:05.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是赢了你 弟弟们就可以填饱肚子了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了弟弟们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:19.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.55,0:17:32.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点投降的话 不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.24,0:17:35.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:39.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.84,0:17:44.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我越使劲她力气就更大
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.11,0:17:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是找到美莉姆 就和她一起吃顿美味大餐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.54,0:17:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天赚了不少 预算足够了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候没机会交给哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.58,0:18:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想着总有一天要给她 一直带在身边
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:17.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山茶花的花语是「强大与骄傲」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.46,0:18:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和哥哥真衬
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.84,0:18:37.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再继续的话 我就要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.01,0:18:43.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.60,0:18:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.41,0:18:51.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.96,0:18:55.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.09,0:19:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于该命运的邂逅了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温迪 要救哥哥了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.56,0:19:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.15,0:19:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火箭飞拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.98,0:19:47.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在就来 姐姐大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.74,0:20:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤依特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:04.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么美莉姆会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.19,0:20:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.48,0:20:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那名斗士到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.29,0:20:30.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就是我正在找的朋友 美莉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.42,0:20:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤依特的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的美莉姆不是那样的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她既关心家人又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.63,0:20:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人一定是知道了她生活拮据 才强迫她
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷了魔导石的 也一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.92,0:20:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那股不可思议的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.04,0:20:55.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或许与希昂大人的魔导石有关联
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.87,0:21:04.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是为了这个目的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:08.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢铁参谋·优米尔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:23.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.23,0:21:26.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去盖纳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:30.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.12,0:21:58.07,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正義の剣は折れ 無機質に転がった
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.34,0:22:03.44,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支えてた自分 reasonとか 見えなくなってしまうの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:08.61,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左手で掴んでも 右手からこぼれて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.00,0:22:13.70,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泣いてなんかいないのに 霞んで行く情景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.86,0:22:18.99,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ゆらり揺れて 惑わす世界はきっと
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.45,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来切符を探してる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.18,0:22:29.50,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鈍い音に 焦らされるように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.67,0:22:33.68,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走り出さなきゃ ゴールはない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.90,0:22:40.00,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,future is serious! future is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.21,0:22:45.41,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,なんで、どうして、心が邪魔をするの?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.57,0:22:47.78,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,future is serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.99,0:22:57.19,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何十回繰り返しても 戸惑いを振り払って
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.46,0:23:07.27,edjap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立ち上がる まだ夢を見たまま…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.10,0:23:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钢铁参谋·优米尔大人竟然对我的身体做那种实验
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.86,0:23:19.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我早说了我当不了斗士了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.50,0:23:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安妮洛特姐姐大人不快点投降的话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.40,0:23:25.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就再也忍不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.12,0:23:30.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但为了妈妈她们 必须要努力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.89,0:23:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一话 盖纳斯城的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骗人 那里绑成那样子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.01,0:23:37.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道龙战士是...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.86,0:23:39.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超级受虐狂吗

